<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=361&amp;p=377#p377"><![CDATA[
2/8(Sat.)Impact of Smartphones over Society/Is the Gogoro Station really harmful to the environment? (Host: Cecillia)<br /><br /><span style="font-weight: bold">Article 1<br />Impact of Smartphones over Society</span><br /><br /><a href="https://www.keyideasinfotech.com/blog/impact-of-smartphone-on-society/" class="postlink">https://www.keyideasinfotech.com/blog/impact-of-smartphone-on-society/</a><br /><br />Questions<br /><br />1. How smart phone changes your life?<br />2. What do you do with your smartphone?<br />3. Is there any negative effect that smartphones cause?<br /><br />////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////<br /><span style="font-weight: bold">Article 2<br />Is the Gogoro Station really harmful to the environment?</span><br /><br /><a href="https://newsbeezer.com/taiwaneng/is-the-gogoro-station-really-harmful-to-the-environment-this-real-data-tells-you-the-truth-about-the-exchange-system-technews/" class="postlink">https://newsbeezer.com/taiwaneng/is-the-gogoro-station-really-harmful-to-the-environment-this-real-data-tells-you-the-truth-about-the-exchange-system-technews/</a><br /><br /><br /><br />Questions<br /><br />1. What concern does Gwangyang have?<br />2. Is Gogoro an eco-friendly product?<br />3. Do you know any government policy related to electric scooters?<br /><br /><br />Agenda<br />7:00 ~ 7:30 pm greetings &amp; free talk<br />7:30 ~ 8:15 pm guests introduced &amp; first session discussion<br />8:15 ~ 8:45 pm presentation, sharing the article &amp; other experiences<br />8:45 ~ 9:30 pm second session discussion<br /><br />Position: Dante coffee Shop (丹堤咖啡), MRT板南線 - 新埔站2號出口, next to 7-Seven,<br />板橋民生路二段237 號,<br />Time: PM 7:00-9:30,<br />a minimum charge of Dante coffee for Royal English club attendant NT$80 (丹提低消80元)<br />最自由的全英文會話聚會,前三次不用交會費,加入會員終生會費NT$500.請帶著開放與熱情來學英文<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=12531">Danny Lin</a> — Thu Feb